# template-build scratch (transcoded clips, manifest) — regenerated on demand
apps/web/scripts/templates/.work/
# full-precision extractor output (~17MB) — the committed runtime copy is the
# quantised apps/web/public/games/alphabet-templates.json
apps/web/src/lib/games/alphabet-templates.json
